---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Quality & Compliance" currentPage="/services/quality-regulatory-compliance">
  <PageHero
    icon="services"
    title="Quality & Regulatory Compliance"
    description="Streamline operations, reduce risks, and stay compliant with evolving requirements."
  />

  <section class="intro-section section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-split">
        <div class="intro-content">
          <h2>Quality Compliance</h2>
          <p>Quality management has a far-reaching impact across all facets of your businessâ€”from R&D and clinical trials to manufacturing and distribution. Consolidating quality management within an enterprise platform streamlines operations, enabling greater efficiency and effectiveness, along with reductions in risks and costs.</p>
          <p>This approach aligns with your most significant business objectives: introducing new products, improving patient safety, fostering collaboration with partners, and staying compliant with evolving regulatory requirements.</p>
          <p>Minimize the burden, mitigate risks, and trim the expenses associated with quality compliance. Our customized solutions offer the capability to automate a single process or enhance your complete quality management system.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="intro-content">
          <h2>Regulatory Compliance</h2>
          <p>Global regulations continue to evolve, with thousands being introduced each year, making compliance both expensive and intricate.</p>
          <p>Our Regulatory Compliance solutions ensure you remain on course and in command. Our operational framework assists in aligning with industry standards. Our team of digital technology experts aids in independent validation services and the development of regulatory applications.</p>
          <p>Our approach centers on best practices encompassing information security management, FDA guidelines on system validation, and electronic records and signatures.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="services-section section section-light">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="services-split">
        <div class="services-left">
          <h3>What we do</h3>
          <div class="service-items">
            <div class="service-item">
              <h4>Quality Management Systems</h4>
              <p>QMS design, implementation, and optimization for ISO 13485 and FDA compliance.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-item">
              <h4>Regulatory Strategy</h4>
              <p>Global regulatory planning and submission support for FDA, EU MDR, and international markets.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-item">
              <h4>Audit Readiness</h4>
              <p>Preparation for FDA inspections, notified body audits, and ISO certifications.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-item">
              <h4>CAPA Management</h4>
              <p>Effective corrective and preventive action systems that drive continuous improvement.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-item">
              <h4>Risk Management</h4>
              <p>ISO 14971 compliance and comprehensive risk assessment programs.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-item">
              <h4>Post-Market Surveillance</h4>
              <p>Vigilance, complaint handling, and regulatory reporting systems.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="services-right">
          <div class="expertise-card">
            <h4>Regulatory Expertise</h4>
            <p>Deep experience with global regulations:</p>
            <ul class="expertise-list">
              <li>FDA 21 CFR Part 820, 210/211</li>
              <li>EU MDR and IVDR</li>
              <li>ISO 13485 and ISO 9001</li>
              <li>Health Canada</li>
              <li>MDSAP</li>
              <li>International requirements</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-card">
        <div class="cta-content">
          <h2>We invest time to fully understand your needs</h2>
          <p>Let's discuss how we can strengthen your quality and compliance systems.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/contact-us" class="btn">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .intro-section {
    background: #fff;
  }

  .intro-split {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .intro-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .intro-content p {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .intro-content p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .services-split {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .services-left h3 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .service-items {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-item {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .service-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    border-color: transparent;
  }

  .service-item h4 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .service-item p {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .expertise-card {
    background: var(--gradient-dark);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    color: #fff;
    position: sticky;
    top: 100px;
  }

  .expertise-card h4 {
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .expertise-card > p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .expertise-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .expertise-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.625rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    padding: 0.625rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .expertise-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .expertise-list li::before {
    content: '';
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--color-accent-light);
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .cta-section {
    background: #fff;
  }

  .cta-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 2rem;
    background: var(--gradient-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: 3rem 4rem;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
  }

  .cta-card .btn {
    background: var(--color-white);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .intro-split {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .services-split {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .expertise-card {
      position: static;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .service-items {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .cta-card {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2.5rem;
    }

    .cta-card .btn {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
